{"tid":2409361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸首都　幾十個被囚押數天的學生終於釋放　要求釋放其餘人士","createTime":"2021-02-15T17:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T18:06:25.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d637c91b169cf144357c8315b3bed9573553d2ec","tid":2409361,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158818802135491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbencrox%2Fposts%2F10158818802135491&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=0b85a6e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158818802135491</a><br />\n<br />\n我望左好多 Post ﹐暫時啲緬民對開槍唔係感到害怕﹐怕嘅人當然有﹐但好多人係就咁行過﹐有部份較勇的會去一直追拍槍手﹐上到網就由其他網民去起底。開完槍條街同家陣六七點旺角咁上下﹐一樣人來人往﹐有人八掛又有細路出街玩⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCalvin Chan:<br />\n因為唔怕冇咗條命？<br />\n<br />\nBen Crox:<br />\n唔知﹐或者人地就係咁膽粗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKyaw Si Thu:<br />\nIts not afraid, its saving strength. There is no point of holding position.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158818813110491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbencrox%2Fposts%2F10158818813110491&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=dc2c6cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bencrox/posts/10158818813110491</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸首都奈比都﹐幾十個因示威被囚押數天的學生終於釋放了出來﹐當地人繼續在監獄外示威﹐要求釋放其餘人士。目前仍有大批民盟執政時的官員和地方首長、醫生被囚押。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1Q8K1z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1Q8K1z.png&h=1abf00d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82a7bd006cd16afd090b39583e7a04be7d628b98","tid":2409361,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"[Old news] VOA: 美國多位參議員重推法案 為港人躲避國安法提供避風港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409348</a>"}]}